'''Thulpin''' was the name of the [[Summer/Legends|summer]] [[growing season]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Draenell's Point]]. Due to the local [[Standard year/Legends|year]] on Draenell's Point lasting for 4.2 standard years, Thulpin lasted for fourteen [[Standard month/Legends|standard months]], accounting for a quarter of Draenell's Point's [[Orbit/Legends|orbital]] cycle.

